    "sections": [
      {
        "sectionId": "19128",
        "sectionNo": "1",
        "orderNo": 1,
        "title": "Short title.",
        "content": "This Act may be called the United Nations (Privileges and Immunities) Act, 1947.",
        "footnotes": "",
        "query": "abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_10_10_00015_194746_1517807324722&sectionId=19128&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_10_10_00015_194746_1517807324722"
      },
      {
        "sectionId": "19129",
        "sectionNo": "2",
        "orderNo": 2,
        "title": "Conferment on United Nations and its representatives and officers and certain privileges and immunities.",
        "content": "(1) Notwithstanding anything to the country contained in any other law, the provisions set\nout in the Schedule to this Act of the Convention on the Privileges and Immunities, adopted by the\nGeneral Assembly of the United Nations on the 13th day of February, 1946, shall have the force of Law\nin India.\n\n(2) The Central Government may, from time to time, by notification in the Official Gazette, amend\nthe Schedule in conformity with any amendments, duly made and adopted, of the provisions of the said\nConvention set out therein.",
        "footnotes": "",
        "query": "abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_10_10_00015_194746_1517807324722&sectionId=19129&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_10_10_00015_194746_1517807324722"
      },
      {
        "sectionId": "19130",
        "sectionNo": "3",
        "orderNo": 3,
        "title": "Power to confer certain privileges and immunities on other international organisations and their representatives and officers.",
        "content": "Where in pursuance of any international agreement, convention or\nother instrument it is necessary to accord to any international organisation and its representatives and\nofficers privileges and immunities in India similar to those contained in the provisions set out in the\nSchedule, the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, declare that the provisions\nset out in the schedule shall, subject to such modification, if any it may consider necessary or expedient\nfor giving effect to the said agreement, convention or other instrument, apply mutatis mutandis to the\ninternational organisation specified in the notification and its representatives and officers, and thereupon\nthe said provisions shall apply accordingly and, notwithstanding anything to the contrary contained in any\nother law, shall in such application have the force of law in India.",
        "footnotes": "",
        "query": "abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_10_10_00015_194746_1517807324722&sectionId=19130&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_10_10_00015_194746_1517807324722"
      },
      {
        "sectionId": "19131",
        "sectionNo": "4",
        "orderNo": 4,
        "title": "Power to make rules.",
        "content": "^1[(1)] The Central Government may ^2[by notification in the Official\nGazette] make rules for carrying out the purposes of this Act.\n\n^2[(2) Every rule made under this Act shall be laid, as soon as may be after it is made, before each\nHouse of Parliament, while it is in session, for a total period of thirty days which may be comprised in\none session or in two or more successive sessions aforesaid, both Houses agree in making any\nmodification in the rule or both Houses agree that the rule should not be made, the rule shall thereafter\nhave effect only in such modified form or be of no effect, as the case may be; so, however, that any such\nmodification or annulment shall be without prejudice to the validity of anything previously done under\nthat rule.]",
        "footnotes": "1. Section 4 renumbered as sub-section (1) thereof by Act 4 of 1986, s. 2 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 15-5-1986).\n\n2. Ins. by s. 2, ibid. (w.e.f. 15-5-1986).",
        "query": "abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_10_10_00015_194746_1517807324722&sectionId=19131&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_10_10_00015_194746_1517807324722"
      }
    ],
    "hindiTitle": "संयुक्‍त राष्‍ट्र (विशेषाधिकर और उन्‍मुक्‍ति)अधिनियम,1947",
    "actYear": "1947",
    "ministry": "Ministry of External Affairs",
    "longTitle": "An Act to give effect to the Convection on the Privileges and immunities of the United Nations.",
    "enforcementDate": "20-12-1947"
  }
